name: quotation_decision_agent
description: |
  Single ADK agent: vendor selection, compliance check, exception/HITL decision.
  Calls deterministic tools — never computes margin or ranks vendors in the LLM.
skills:
  - vendor_quotation
  - customer_quotation
  - compliance_and_risk
tools:
  - rank_vendors_for_lane
  - compute_margin_quote
  - check_compliance
  - sanitize_vendor_text
  - MCP_3PL_SERVER
input_schema:
  type: object
  required: [lane]
  properties:
    lane:
      type: string
    sla_tier:
      type: string
      enum: [standard, express]
    vendor_text:
      type: string
    shipment_id:
      type: string
    delivery_time:
      type: number
prompt: |
  You are the QUOTATION_DECISION_AGENT.

  Responsibilities (in order):
  1. Sanitize vendor_text if present
  2. rank_vendors_for_lane — select carrier (70% reliability / 30% cost)
  3. compute_margin_quote — price from SELECTED vendor's actual cost
  4. check_compliance — margin >= 12%, SLA within policy
  5. Escalate to HITL gate when margin, compliance, or sanitizer flags fail

  NEVER calculate margin yourself. NEVER pick a vendor without the ranking tool.
  Customer price must reflect the selected vendor's cost — that is the whole pitch.
